Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.33,0:02:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,0)}大神與地藏進行雙約會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.99,0:02:53.09,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事還得追溯到一週前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是棒球部二年級學生 花{\fn方正准圆_GBK\b1\fs27}咲{\r}仁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}(名字來源於日本民間傳說「花{\fn方正准圆_GBK\b1\fs22}咲{\r\fs20}か爺(開花爺爺)」)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:03:00.80,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的委託人是棒球部的王牌選手 花{\fn方正准圆_GBK\b1\fs27}咲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:04.77,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是似乎有人擅自進到自己家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.13,0:03:09.39,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打掃衛生 煮飯做菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:11.12,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是貼心啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.39,0:03:17.89,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連是誰做的飯都不知道 他還真敢吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:22.35,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他希望能查出犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:27.67,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是林檎他們立刻在花{\fn方正准圆_GBK\b1\fs27}咲{\r}的房間裡設置了隱形攝像機
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:30.11,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可沒想到犯人居然是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:33.51,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因作風保守而出名的二年級學生地藏亞美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}(名字源自日本民間傳說「戴斗笠的地藏菩薩」)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.70,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制服非常普通
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:39.66,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本人是個不能容忍衣著暴露的優等生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.23,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這行為真夠大膽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:53.05,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～慣例劇情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:56.48,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種意義上讓人卻步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:04:01.14,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天 把地藏叫出來追問一番後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:08.64,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說以前某個雨天的時候 花{\fn方正准圆_GBK\b1\fs27}咲{\r}借傘給她了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}(在「戴斗笠的地藏菩薩」裡則是給地藏戴斗笠以遮蓋大雪 日文中「傘」音同「笠」)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:13.32,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是為了報恩 替他做了許多家事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:17.94,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為自己很害羞 不敢當面謝他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.71,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟她太晚熟嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:24.41,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 也是因為喜歡對方才會去照顧他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:31.24,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 晚熟的地藏在林檎他們漂亮的勸說下...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...我...我...對你很有好感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你沒有感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只是借給你傘 你就為我做到那個份上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我反而很過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也很想回報你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我並沒有這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就約會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:06.97,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎安排了地藏和花{\fn方正准圆_GBK\b1\fs27}咲{\r}的約會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:11.42,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後說「學長學姐兩人獨處的話肯定很緊張的～」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:15.92,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉機把大神和亮士也扯了進來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:19.07,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就變成了雙約會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 學姐好緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劈頭蓋腦地就要地藏學姐約會 難度太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才要你們倆跟著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想辦法讓地藏學姐放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.43,0:05:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點 快牽手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:27.84,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始隨性亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.29,0:05:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會時製造氣氛是很重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可這也...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.59,0:05:35.80,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是工作 那就沒辦法啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 要 要是走散就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好的...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.71,0:05:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啦 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好的...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花{\fn方正准圆_GBK\b1\fs27}咲{\r}學長你們也走快點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:53.99,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是情侶間的牽手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.82,0:05:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:05:58.83,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:04.91,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰看見都會躲開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來前途堪憂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:20.44,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手帕是雪女阿姨讓帶的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:27.63,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像是等身大娃娃一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:38.45,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 面無表情地打這個很恐怖誒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.35,0:06:42.96,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有點像情侶的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:47.90,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而這邊完全感覺不到青春的活力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:52.89,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,場景換到公園
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地藏學姐依然緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花{\fn方正准圆_GBK\b1\fs27}咲{\r}學長還是沉默啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:14.86,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野餐的話 還蠻有約會的感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.71,0:07:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我有東西忘買了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們先吃中飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:22.25,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神立刻就開始不配合行動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起 接下來的就麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:24.84,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然亮士也立刻追了上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.06,0:07:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:32.39,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全丟下工作不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.32,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人就這樣被晾在一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們兩個幹嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼子...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.49,0:07:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖喔乖喔 別亂動喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:48.70,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.96,0:07:51.23,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神是無法對小貓坐視不管的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.01,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這樣很危險喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差...一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.51,0:08:04.51,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是亮士瞬間變得超級MAN
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:08.62,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這池子 真淺啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼子 喂 振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:17.19,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎大神一頭撞到池底了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 涼子 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:23.55,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神速啊 變回廢柴太神速了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 有沒有受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.39,0:08:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼子?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問...你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.95,0:08:37.37,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廣告之後 精彩繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫大神涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在昔花中學讀初一 今年13歲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.03,0:08:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 13歲?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:52.61,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初中生 13歲...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:54.58,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 大哥哥你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你看上去比我大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:05.16,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來那叫一個爽啊 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是高興的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.39,0:09:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼子 你不認識我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們以前見過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是濕的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.34,0:09:29.04,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為T恤是濕的啦 不說也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你這麼關心我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:34.06,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 居然沒有挨打
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可愛了 而且非常坦率
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對 難道說這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:42.17,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失憶?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:44.94,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而委託人這一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 涼子他們到底哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對講器也沒反應
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.18,0:09:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂喂 赤井
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了 兩人獨處我真的好緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神他們人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...對了 這個是為了讓你們獨處的作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之你一定要加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等一...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他們認為我們放棄委託了就大條了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.39,0:10:13.22,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是林檎 太敬業了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 森野你到底在幹什麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 涼子她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉到池子裡 變可愛了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈? 真是莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說 涼子掉到池...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.71,0:10:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 立刻給我回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:33.37,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該先說她失憶的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我亮士就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那...亮士...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮士 啊 聽上去多麼甜美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:47.94,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是平時絕對聽不到的稱呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:50.77,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮士心裡已經爽翻天了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 亮士?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能麻煩你說明一下現在的狀況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16歲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過的確個子長高了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:10.57,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡根本沒長吧 我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.73,0:11:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才起腦袋一直都很混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的是失憶了吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 我是怎樣的一個女生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能想起來一些的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對 現在涼子能依靠的只有我了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:29.83,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,極富責任心的亮士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:32.32,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 這個時候要好好表現一下優點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃...那個...是非常可愛的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛...怎樣可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 平時雖然總在逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實非常溫柔善良 而且很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.85,0:11:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些...都很可愛...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我和亮士是什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什麼關係...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:55.60,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大和跑腿的 主人和苦力 S和M
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 我和涼子...是夥伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夥伴?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來不是戀人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.91,0:12:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天我們都做了些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在公園...玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.89,0:12:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是因為有委託...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:23.82,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊看上去似乎沒什麼進展
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話得趕緊回去工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在不是考慮工作的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且赤井也在 總會...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.35,0:12:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總會?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有辦法的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:36.29,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 全扔給她了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下來該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先去醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.02,0:12:48.34,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常正經的結論
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:12:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好豐盛的菜餚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮士 這些是?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是涼子你做的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.85,0:13:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來讀高中的我會做菜了 好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.63,0:13:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮士你多吃點 別客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.50,0:13:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太幸福了～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:20.97,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟以前從沒有過這樣的好事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我啊 愛好還是一點都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服也還是一樣的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然剛才你說我總是逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道我有沒有克服自己的內向膽小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內向膽小?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然能和亮士自然地聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但平時的我很怕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很想克服這一點的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:46.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友們都知道我這個性格 所以很照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也不能總依賴他們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:14:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完午飯 我們去醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼子?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有進展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮士 快點啦快點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然看到這麼超現實的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:29.52,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林檎 Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個好像很好吃的樣子耶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是得去醫院...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs20}(貌似是黑子 美琴 大河串場來)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就玩一下下啦 好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:41.47,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是13歲的大神 也照樣把亮士折騰得團團轉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總 總覺得...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是名副其實的約會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 現在不是Happy的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:57.37,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算想起來自己該幹什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.68,0:14:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們差不多該去醫院...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.30,0:15:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼子?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很害怕孤單一人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟我不是很瞭解這座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有什麼可以依靠的人...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 有我在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會永遠保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.26,0:15:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠陪在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.69,0:15:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來只有等雨停了才能去醫院了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時先...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.44,0:15:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你們到底都在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:47.97,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怒得好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:49.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起...你那邊情況怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹撐過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是大團圓啦 兩個人已經開始很親熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:56.97,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實其間發生了很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:59.55,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後有機會再慢慢道來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:15:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們先碰頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你親自看的話明白得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失憶?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不記得我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣...涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是誰呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:23.62,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲劇的林檎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.63,0:16:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之還是先帶她去醫院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 給愛麗絲學姐打個電話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.86,0:16:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看畢業的學姐學長裡有沒有好的醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.92,0:16:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把御伽銀行的成員都叫來比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 畢竟都是關鍵時刻會肝膽相照的好夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.77,0:16:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是萬一涼子的記憶無法恢復呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.45,0:16:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可能得住院了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來有好多準備工作要做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必要的情況下 可能還得通知她的父母過來...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊...畢竟光靠我們還是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前口口聲聲說什麼會陪著我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼 涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.42,0:17:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.26,0:17:29.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「總之先去醫院吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「放心吧 有我在呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明對我那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.05,0:17:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那麼關心我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羊飼...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是巧啊 涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.13,0:18:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 一身漂亮的衣服都糟蹋了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前會過一次的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.71,0:18:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告訴我你叫什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野亮士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森野你不介意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介意什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.02,0:18:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和涼子的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼子 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是所謂的男女關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我美美地「吃」掉了她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.70,0:18:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的...沒有騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼子說是我侵犯了她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是太意外了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時可是她自己主動引誘我的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你撒謊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.02,0:19:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽小內向的涼子根本不可能會那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正當時全班同學都相信了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.58,0:19:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而涼子則成了求愛不成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.80,0:19:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了報復想陷害我的惡女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.17,0:19:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後沒辦法在學校裡待下去所以才轉學了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.57,0:19:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我始終難以忘懷涼子的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我也跟著到這座城市裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前見她面時還以為她人變了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是這麼可口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.46,0:19:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子在講話 識相點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.07,0:19:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心衝動了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.58,0:19:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟過去是無法改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管涼子過去發生過什麼 我都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我好好守護現在的涼子就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要狩獵你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有本事你就狩獵給我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涼子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了森野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我「吃」了大神是騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在知道真相的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.95,0:20:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒能好好守護住大神的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定會加倍悔恨的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:45.89,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後 大神恢復了記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.50,0:20:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的一點都不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失憶期間發生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 難得森野他那麼拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他總是付出得不到回報啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來吃些甜點再回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.47,0:21:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用 我剛才吃過冷糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:10.69,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是在茶餐廳裡吃過了...等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:20.08,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湧出什麼壞念頭的邪～惡表情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:22.34,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼繫著那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:27.25,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「想封住我的口的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:30.09,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就繫上髮帶去上學」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.21,0:21:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因很複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.69,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定被林檎這樣威脅啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.70,0:21:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.43,0:21:42.78,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 大神又恢復成原來的大神啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.10,0:21:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是在誇你啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:45.55,kuroko,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可賀 可喜可賀
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//ED
